                    <li>☐ Exposure class (C-1, C-2, etc.)</li>
                    <li>☐ Maximum aggregate size</li>
                    <li>☐ Slump range (mm)</li>
                    <li>☐ Air content if required (%)</li>
                    <li>☐ Any special requirements</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Delivery Details:</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li>☐ Total quantity (m³)</li>
                    <li>☐ Delivery rate (m³/hour)</li>
                    <li>☐ Pour sequence/locations</li>
                    <li>☐ Access restrictions</li>
                    <li>☐ Pump required?</li>
                    <li>☐ Hot/cold weather plan</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 mt-6">
                <p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">
                  Example Order: "32 MPa, C-1 exposure, 14mm aggregate, 100mm slump, 6% air, 
                  40 m³ for driveway, need 10 m³/hour, pump required, delivery Tuesday 7 AM"
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
